# Cricket Fielding Performance Analysis

This project analyzes cricket fielding performance including catches, run-outs, and overall fielding efficiency.

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns

data = {
    "Player": ["Babar", "Rohit", "Dhoni", "Gill", "Hardik"],
    "Matches": [100, 95, 120, 50, 70],
    "Catches": [85, 78, 90, 40, 60],
    "Run_Outs": [15, 10, 25, 8, 18]
}

df = pd.DataFrame(data)

# Total dismissals
df["Total_Dismissals"] = df["Catches"] + df["Run_Outs"]

# Fielding efficiency per match
df["Efficiency_per_Match"] = df["Total_Dismissals"] / df["Matches"]

df

sns.barplot(x="Player", y="Catches", data=df)
plt.title("Catches by Player")
plt.show()

## Conclusion

- Dhoni has the highest total dismissals.
- Virat and Rohit also show strong fielding performance.
- Efficiency per match helps measure consistency.
- Fielding analysis helps identify best defensive players.

